<h1 id="page-title">Glossary &amp; grievance phone tree</h1>

<section aria-labelledby="glossary-heading">
  <h2 id="glossary-heading">Glossary</h2>
  <dl>
    {{#each terms}}
      <dt><strong>{{term}}</strong></dt>
      <dd>{{definition}}</dd>
    {{/each}}
  </dl>
</section>

<section aria-labelledby="phone-tree-heading">
  <h2 id="phone-tree-heading">Grievance phone tree</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Hospital grievance desk — file in writing, keep the stamped acknowledgement.</li>
    <li>TPA grievance cell — call the helpline on <code>DOC-001</code>.</li>
    <li>Insurer grievance officer — contact details in your policy document.</li>
    <li>IRDAI Bima Bharosa — <strong>155255</strong> or <strong>complaints@irdai.gov.in</strong>.</li>
    <li>Insurance Ombudsman (zone-wise) — see <code>cioins.co.in</code>.</li>
  </ol>
</section>
